---
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="badge">v0.3</div>
    <p class="pain">Agent Skills are scattered. Installing them shouldn't be risky.</p>
    <h1>
      One command to <span class="accent">fetch</span>, <span class="accent">scan</span>, and <span class="accent">run</span> any Agent Skill.
    </h1>
    <p class="tagline">
      skillx pulls skills from any Git host or directory, scans them with 23 security rules,
      injects into your agent, and auto-cleans when done.
    </p>

    <div class="terminal-wrapper">
      <div class="terminal-glow"></div>
      <div class="terminal">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <div class="dots">
            <span class="dot red"></span>
            <span class="dot yellow"></span>
            <span class="dot green"></span>
          </div>
          <span class="terminal-title">terminal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
          <div class="line">
            <span class="prompt">$</span>
            <span class="cmd typing">skillx run github:anthropics/skills/pdf-processing "Extract tables"</span>
          </div>
          <div class="line output delay-1">
            <span class="cyan">→</span> Resolving source...
          </div>
          <div class="line output delay-2">
            <span class="green">✓</span> Resolved: pdf-processing
          </div>
          <div class="line output delay-3">
            <span class="cyan">→</span> Scanning for security issues...
          </div>
          <div class="line output delay-4">
            <span class="green">✓</span> Scan Result: <span class="green">PASS</span> <span class="dim">(23 rules checked)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="line output delay-5">
            <span class="green">✓</span> Using agent: Claude Code
          </div>
          <div class="line output delay-6">
            <span class="green">✓</span> Injected 3 files to .claude/skills/pdf-processing
          </div>
          <div class="line output delay-7">
            <span class="cyan">→</span> Launching agent...
          </div>
          <div class="line output delay-8">
            <span class="dim">  [Claude Code running...]</span>
          </div>
          <div class="line output delay-9">
            <span class="green">✓</span> Agent completed. Cleanup done.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-group">
      <a href="/getting-started/" class="cta-primary">Get Started</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/skillx-run/skillx" class="cta-secondary">View on GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
    color: #a5b4fc;
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pain {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .accent {
    color: #6366f1;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  /* Terminal with glow */
  .terminal-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .terminal-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -2px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5), rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3), rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5));
    filter: blur(16px);
    opacity: 0.6;
    z-index: -1;
    animation: glowPulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes glowPulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; filter: blur(16px); }
    50% { opacity: 0.8; filter: blur(22px); }
  }

  .terminal {
    background: #0c1222;
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.25);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1),
      0 0 30px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08),
      0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .terminal-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: #0f172a;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1e293b;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .dot.red { background: #ef4444; }
  .dot.yellow { background: #eab308; }
  .dot.green { background: #22c55e; }

  .terminal-title {
    color: #475569;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: 1.25rem;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .line {
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .prompt {
    color: #6366f1;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .cmd {
    color: #e2e8f0;
  }

  .output {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease forwards;
  }

  .cyan { color: #22d3ee; }
  .green { color: #22c55e; }
  .dim { color: #475569; }

  .delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  .delay-2 { animation-delay: 1.3s; }
  .delay-3 { animation-delay: 1.8s; }
  .delay-4 { animation-delay: 2.5s; }
  .delay-5 { animation-delay: 3.2s; }
  .delay-6 { animation-delay: 3.8s; }
  .delay-7 { animation-delay: 4.4s; }
  .delay-8 { animation-delay: 5.0s; }
  .delay-9 { animation-delay: 6.5s; }

  .typing {
    overflow: hidden;
    border-right: 2px solid #6366f1;
    white-space: nowrap;
    animation:
      typing 1.5s steps(70) forwards,
      blink 0.8s step-end 3;
    width: 0;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  @keyframes typing {
    to { width: 100%; }
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    50% { border-color: transparent; }
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    background: #6366f1;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .cta-primary:hover {
    background: #4f46e5;
  }

  .cta-secondary {
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .cta-secondary:hover {
    border-color: #6366f1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    .hero {
      padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
    }
    .terminal-body {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .terminal-glow {
      filter: blur(12px);
    }
  }
</style>
